author: Sean Quinton
title: Media reaction: Seahawks return to form in 20-3 win over 49ers
text:
“Winning feels good”.
After Thursday’s dominant 20-3 win over the 49ers, a sense of relief could be felt across social media as fans and media members witnessed the Seahawks return to form. Marshawn Lynch ran for more than 100 yards, the defense was stifling, sacking Colin Kaepernick 6 times and allowed just 142 yards of offense, and the team finally held a fourth-quarter lead after failing to do so in four losses this season.
In a season defined by turmoil and consternation, Thursday night was a much-needed step in the right direction for the Seahawks. Here’s how fans and media members reacted to the win:
